eo class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2374010/extras/7ddfc7c8a01c0f154f4699b2b4169540.poster.avif?t=1716377284\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2374010/extras/7ddfc7c8a01c0f154f4699b2b4169540.webm?t=1716377284\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2374010/extras/7ddfc7c8a01c0f154f4699b2b4169540.mp4?t=1716377284\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Your <strong>SKILLS </strong>and <strong>REFLEXES </strong>will be tested as your <strong>FIGHT </strong>through <strong>EARTH </strong>and <strong>SPACE</strong>!<br>If you're looking for a <strong>FAST </strong>and <strong>EXCITING </strong>Action Game, then <strong>Tenders Fight</strong> is for <strong><u>YOU</u></strong>.",
